The following distro packages are required for use of SquidInk:
    redis
    python-redis

The following Python packages (install with easy_install, pip, or similar)
are also required:
    PyRSS2Gen
    markdown
    flask

The following packages are recommended, but not necessary (the functions they provide will simply be disabled if they're not present):
    statusnet (from IdentiCurse, or alternatively an interface-compatible module)
    pygments
